        name: "Sleeplessness",
        desc: "A healer who once slumbered for a century now offers to treat your sleeplessness.",
        memoryName: "Essentials of Medicinal Herbs",
        memoryDesc: "A compendium cataloguing 1,890 medicinal substances — nearly half of them herbs. The author's name reads: Fufeng.",
        reward: 7050,
